{"tid":1913781,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"武漢展開「感恩教育」 籲市民「感恩總書記、感恩共產黨」","createTime":"2020-03-07T05:26:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T12:38:25.000Z","uid":39464,"like":7,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"f35c513dc3611a6f5da00ab90d28322b3221053a","tid":1913781,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T05:26:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/03/07/phpmoBAnY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F03%2F07%2FphpmoBAnY.jpg&h=2bc9d3b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國武漢爆發的新型冠狀病毒疾病（COVID-19，下稱武漢肺炎）疫情持續延燒，中國武漢市委書記王忠林昨（6）日晚間宣布，要對全市廣大市民展開「感恩教育」，呼籲市民「感恩總書記、感恩共產黨」，並且「聽黨話、跟黨走，形成強大正能量」。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，王忠林表示，武漢市全面對抗武漢肺炎疫情這幾個月以來，「在習近平總書記親自部署、親自指揮和黨中央堅強領導下，解放軍及全國各地先後派出數百支醫療隊，數萬名醫務工作者集結馳援武漢，全國捐贈物資源源不斷」。<br />\n<br />\n王忠林強調，「武漢人民是英雄的人民，也是懂得感恩的人民」，因此要在廣大市民與黨員幹部中展開「感恩教育」，呼籲市民「感恩總書記、感恩共產黨」，並且「聽黨話、跟黨走，形成強大正能量」，還要「宣傳群眾、發動群眾、依靠群眾，做好疫情防控工作」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3091820\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3091820&d=nExaWN1d7lalHJLKFoHQnEYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=5b017951\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3091820&h=c6f49f20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3091820</a>"},{"pid":"89caf3203b2081ebea3ba9138477dfec7e0b8c70","tid":1913781,"uid":20928,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T05:34:27.000Z","msg":"連肺炎大爆發都要感謝黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />洗唔洗玩咁盡呀"},{"pid":"67008b7296ca297f7feae87a3f7b29f985466919","tid":1913781,"uid":89752,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T05:40:40.000Z","msg":"香港都要<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽黨話，跟黨走"},{"pid":"9c